description: In April 2014, Dutch tourists Kris Kremers and Lisanne Froon disappeared while hiking in Panama. Despite extensive search efforts, their fate remains a chilling enigma. This video delves into the haunting details of their last moments and the eerie clues left behind, leaving investigators and the world baffled. Discover the mystery that continues to captivate true crime enthusiasts and outdoor adventurers alike
